class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-getting-to-koh-tao\">Getting to Koh Tao<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You can&#x2019;t fly to Koh Tao but it&#x2019;s best to reach by airplane via Bangkok or Koh Samui.<\/p>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/clk.tradedoubler.com\/click?p=224457&amp;a=2846389&amp;g=20638266&amp;url=https:\/\/www.skyscanner.net\/flights-to\/BKK\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Easily find the cheapest flights tickets to here!<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-sai-nuan-beach\">Sai Nuan Beach<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This beach is only reachable by foot or water taxi. It has a&#xA0;swing&#xA0;and plenty of shade under beautiful coconut palms. There are a couple of bars to grab a drink or snack.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-instagram wp-block-embed-instagram\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/BMFYj-JgCyo\/?taken-at=258391402\n<\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-chalok-baan-kao\">Chalok Baan Kao<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This is the third-largest Koh Tao beach and it&#x2019;s located in the South. In this tiny town, you&#x2019;ll find a 7-Eleven, some dive centers, and restaurants. There is also a turtle&#xA0;conservation program but we weren&#x2019;t able to find it.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-freedom-beach\">Freedom Beach<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the Koh Tao beaches that were a little hard to reach. Located at the southern tip of the island. You have to pass Chalok and Taa Toh Resort until the end of the road. Then walk your way down. There are a lot of trees near the beach which gives it a unique beach view and it provides shade when you need it. There&#x2019;s also a concrete path you can follow that goes around back to Chalok Baan Beach.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/thailand-koh-tao-freedom-beach.jpg\" alt=\"koh tao beaches freedom walk\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"koh tao beaches freedom walk\" class=\"wp-image-1093 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165251\/thailand-koh-tao-freedom-beach.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165251\/thailand-koh-tao-freedom-beach-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165251\/thailand-koh-tao-freedom-beach-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165251\/thailand-koh-tao-freedom-beach-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165251\/thailand-koh-tao-freedom-beach-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165251\/thailand-koh-tao-freedom-beach-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165251\/thailand-koh-tao-freedom-beach-163x122.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165251\/thailand-koh-tao-freedom-beach-240x180.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165251\/thailand-koh-tao-freedom-beach-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165251\/thailand-koh-tao-freedom-beach-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/07\/23165251\/thailand-koh-tao-freedom-beach-30x23.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.pn